<includeonly>{{#invoke:Infobox|item|id={{{id|}}}|image={{{image|}}}}}</includeonly><noinclude>
{{doc}}
Renders an item infobox. Pass the template identifier as <code>id</code>.

Parameters:
* <code>id</code> — item template identifier (required)
* <code>image</code> — image filename, e.g. <code>Iron Ingot.png</code> (optional)
[[Category:Infobox templates]]
